      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Pick at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's been driven and it shows, but it remains a reliable, functional car that gets the job done! The exterior has some visible wear including minor dents and scratches consistent with everyday use, and the interior shows signs of regular use as well. Mechanically, it runs and drives, making it a great option for a budget-conscious buyer who needs dependable transportation without the premium price tag. What you see is what you get \u2014 honest value for an honest price!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
