      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at an honest, competitive price of $31,500. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you'll find only minor surface scratches and perhaps a small scuff or two consistent with normal everyday use, but no significant dents or major paint damage. The interior is clean and well-kept, with moderate wear on the seats and surfaces that you'd expect from a regularly driven vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained appropriately \u2014 no warning lights, no unusual noises, and all major systems are functioning as they should. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for good value without paying a premium for mint condition. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
