      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Wow, what a gem! This car is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 we're talking pristine inside and out, with a flawless interior, spotless exterior, and everything running and looking as close to brand-new as you'll ever find on the used market. There are no signs of significant wear, no mechanical concerns, and the finish gleams like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you've been searching for a used car that truly feels new, this is a rare opportunity you won't want to miss. Come see it for yourself \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 47000.0,
